Subject: [PATCH] Revert "[UNDERTOW-1623] Prevent the deadlock by invoking
 AbstractFramedChannel.lastDataRead() outside of a synchronized block at
 AbstractFramedChannel.receive()."

This reverts commit 846c50ead09f7d0b38965b4726ba0b6c5582bf7f.
